===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abbot}}, {{m|enm|abbod}}, {{m|enm|abbed}}, from {{inh|en|ang|abbat}}, {{m|ang|abbad}}, {{m|ang|abbod}}, from {{der|en|la|abbās||father}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἀββᾶς|sc=polytonic}}, from {{der|en|arc|אבא||father|tr=’abbā|sc=Hebr}}. Compare [[abba]], [[abbé]].

