* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/ˈæb.ət/|lang=en}}
* {{a|GenAm}} {{IPA|/ˈæb.ət/|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-abbot.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}
* {{homophones|Abbot|lang=en}}
